  "title": "QC Inspector",
  "description": "<p>We are from central kitchen in food manufacturing sector located in Singapore, fostering a positive work environment—\"Work Hard, Play Hard!\" We're looking for passionate professionals to join our family!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Position:</strong> QC Inspector</p>\n<p><strong>Monthly Salary: </strong>From $2,500 onwards</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist the Production Manager in planning, coordinating, and supervising daily production activities.</li>\n  <li>Monitor production schedules and adjust operations to meet targets efficiently.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with food safety, hygiene, and quality standards.</li>\n  <li>Support and train production staff, ensuring adherence to operational procedures.</li>\n  <li>Work with the maintenance team to resolve machinery or equipment issues promptly.</li>\n  <li>Maintain production records and prepare reports for management review.</li>\n  <li>Identify areas for process improvement and implement best practices.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with other departments such as quality control, procurement, and logistics.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong attention to detail and analytical skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a team and communicate effectively.</li>\n  <li>Experience with quality testing equipment and documentation.</li>\n  <li>Problem-solving mindset with attention to detail.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p>✔ 20 days of paid leave</p>\n<p>✔ Medical benefits &amp; insurance coverage</p>\n<p>✔ Various allowances &amp; incentives (Meal allowances, Revenue Incentives, etc.)</p>\n<p>✔ Various bonuses (AWS, performance, attendance)</p>\n<p>✔ Various rewards (Best Employee Award, Long services award, etc.)</p>\n<p>✔ Strong career progression opportunities</p>\n<p>✔ Revenue incentives</p>\n<p>✔ Sponsored courses for career growth</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>If you’re the right fit for our team, send your application here! We look forward to your application!</strong></p>",
